# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [0.0.4] - 2024-03-19

### Added
- Debug mode for troubleshooting and development
- Environment variable `DEBUG` to control debug output
- HTML content saving for debugging purposes

### Changed
- Updated scraping logic to work with new Bookshop.org DOM structure
- Updated dependencies to latest versions
- Improved error handling and logging

### Fixed
- Fixed href extraction from search results
- Fixed search results parsing to handle new page layout

## [0.0.3] - 2024-03-19

### Added
- Initial release
- Basic search functionality
- JSON output format
